Como rodar o banco novo:

Rodar Docker compose down & up -d

- Rodar : php artisan migrate --path=database/migrations/credentials --database=credentials
Para rodar a migration do familiaMogi_credentials

- Rodar : php artisan migrate --path=database/migrations/content --database=content
Para rodar a migration do familiaMogi_content

- Rodar : php artisan db:seed